---
title: Mongolian Lamb & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Switch up this Chinese restaurant staple by adding tender lamb mince instead of the usual beef strips. Featuring all of your favourite stir-fried veggies and fluffy garlic rice, you may never want to go back to the original again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mongolian-lamb-veggie-stir-fry-2f4d525f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/mongolian-lamb-veggie-stir-fry-5fbc4f51fed86f67f8213828-cec2dc72.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
